{{Youmay|the [[Blaster/Legends|blaster]] targeting [[Scope/Legends|scope]]|the [[infrared motion sensor]] commonly referred to as a "night scope"}}
{{Otheruses|night}}
'''Night scopes''',<ref name="GFT">''[[Gundark's Fantastic Technology: Personal Gear]]''</ref> also spelled '''nightscopes'''<ref name="JQ">''[[Jedi Quest: The Master of Disguise]]''</ref> or referred to as '''night-vision scopes''', were targeting [[Scope/Legends|scopes]] that allowed an individual to aim better in low-light conditions.<ref name="SWTSE">''[[Star Wars Trilogy Sourcebook, Special Edition]]''</ref> They could be affixed to [[Blaster/Legends|blaster]] weapons to increase their accuracy.<ref name="GFT" /> [[Boba Fett/Legends|Boba Fett]] had a night scope on his [[EE-3 carbine rifle/Legends|EE-3 blaster carbine]].<ref name="SWTSE" />

